# PrimeForm workspace rules (repo boundaries)

- This repo is the APP repo: /primeform-app (frontend + marketing + docs).
- Frontend deploy target is /primeform-frontend (Quasar/Vue). Vercel builds from this folder.
- Do not create submodules. Do not embed other git repos inside this repo.
- Backend lives in a separate sibling repo: /primeform-api (outside this repo).
- Marketing site lives in separate sibling repo: /website-2026 (outside this repo).
- Never refer to any folder named "PrimeForm/" inside the app repo.
